{"title":"Git","uid":"221a7ad001c03569112f684b2dfdc120","slug":"Software/Git","date":"2020-12-25T15:54:04.000Z","updated":"2022-04-06T09:13:39.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Software/Git.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/git.jpeg","content":"<h2 id=\"基本操作\"><a href=\"#基本操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基本操作\"></a>基本操作</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 初始化</span>\n$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> init\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 添加到暂存区</span>\n$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> -A\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 添加到分支</span>\n$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> commit -m <span class=\"token string\">\"deploy\"</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 关联远程仓库，命名为origin</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\"># 1. ssh方式</span>\n$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> remote <span class=\"token function\">add</span> origin git@github.com:Yveltals/test.git\n  <span class=\"token comment\"># 2.https方式</span>\n$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> remote <span class=\"token function\">add</span> origin https://github.com/Yveltals/test.git\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 推送到远程orign仓库，分支main —> main</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\"># 之后不用加 -u</span>\n$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> push -u origin main<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<br/>\n\n<h2 id=\"切换本地用户\"><a href=\"#切换本地用户\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"切换本地用户\"></a>切换本地用户</h2><ol>\n<li><p>查看当前git用户名邮箱：</p>\n <pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> config user.name\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> config user.email<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n<li><p>切换git用户名邮箱: </p>\n <pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> config --global user.name <span class=\"token string\">\"YOURUSERNAME\"</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> config --global user.email <span class=\"token string\">\"YOUREMAIL\"</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n<br/>\n\n<h2 id=\"重新关联远程仓库\"><a href=\"#重新关联远程仓库\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"重新关联远程仓库\"></a>重新关联远程仓库</h2><ol>\n<li><p>查看一下远程仓库的repo 的链接方式，将http方式改成git方式</p>\n <pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> remote show origin<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n<li><p>移除现有的http方式的远程仓库</p>\n <pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> remote <span class=\"token function\">rm</span> origin<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n<li><p>重新添加成<a href=\"mailto:&#x67;&#105;&#x74;&#64;&#x67;&#105;&#x74;&#104;&#x75;&#x62;&#x2e;&#x63;&#111;&#109;\">&#x67;&#105;&#x74;&#64;&#x67;&#105;&#x74;&#104;&#x75;&#x62;&#x2e;&#x63;&#111;&#109;</a>的方式并关联</p>\n <pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> remote <span class=\"token function\">add</span> origin git@github.com:Yveltals/test.git\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> push -u origin main<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n<br/>\n\n<h2 id=\"下载Submodule\"><a href=\"#下载Submodule\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下载Submodule\"></a>下载Submodule</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-git\" data-language=\"git\"><code class=\"language-git\">git submodule init\ngit submodule update --recommend-shallow<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<br/>\n\n<h2 id=\"SSH密钥\"><a href=\"#SSH密钥\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SSH密钥\"></a>SSH密钥</h2><ol>\n<li><p>创建密钥</p>\n <pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class=\"token string\">\"gitHub注册邮箱\"</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n<li><p>查看密钥</p>\n<p> Linux：~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub（公钥）</p>\n<p> window：计算机–&gt;用户–&gt;用户名文件夹–&gt;.ssh–&gt;id_rsa.pub</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>添加密钥</p>\n<p> Settings -&gt; SSH and GPG keys -&gt; New SSH key</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>确定一下ssh-key是否添加成功</p>\n <pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">ssh</span> -T git@github.com<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n<p><br/><br/></p>\n<h2 id=\"文件修改\"><a href=\"#文件修改\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"文件修改\"></a>文件修改</h2><h3 id=\"查看文件\"><a href=\"#查看文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"查看文件\"></a>查看文件</h3><p><code>git log</code>查看文件修改记录，<code>--pretty=oneline</code>简化</p>\n<p><code>git status</code>查看一下状态</p>\n<p><code>git diff filename</code>:比较工作区和暂存区</p>\n<p><code>git diff HEAD -- filename</code>:比较工作区和版本库的最新版本</p>\n<h3 id=\"撤销修改\"><a href=\"#撤销修改\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"撤销修改\"></a>撤销修改</h3><p><code>git checkout -- file</code>:改乱了工作区某个文件的内容，想直接丢弃工作区的修改时</p>\n<p><code>git reset HEAD</code>:不但改乱了工作区还添加到了暂存区时，第一步用该命令，就回到了场景1，第二步按场景1操作</p>\n<h3 id=\"文件删除\"><a href=\"#文件删除\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"文件删除\"></a>文件删除</h3><p><code>rm</code>:删除工作区文件，可从版本库恢复<code>git checkout -- test.txt</code><br><code>git rm;git commit</code>:从版本库删除，不能上边方法恢复</p>\n<br/>\n\n<br/>\n\n<h2 id=\"分支操作\"><a href=\"#分支操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"分支操作\"></a>分支操作</h2><h3 id=\"创建分支\"><a href=\"#创建分支\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"创建分支\"></a>创建分支</h3><p><code>git branch name</code>：创建</p>\n<p><code>git checkout -b name</code>：创建并转到</p>\n<p><code>git checkout -b name origin/name</code>：在本地创建和远程分支对应的分支</p>\n<p><code>git branch --set-upstream name origin/name</code>：建立本地分支和远程分支的关联</p>\n<h3 id=\"合并分支\"><a href=\"#合并分支\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"合并分支\"></a>合并分支</h3><p><code>git branch</code>：查看分支</p>\n<p><code>git switch/checkout name</code>：切换分支</p>\n<p><code>git merge name</code>：将name分支合并到当前分支(新分支合并到老分支)</p>\n<p><code>git branch -d name</code>：删除分支</p>\n<h3 id=\"分支同步\"><a href=\"#分支同步\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"分支同步\"></a>分支同步</h3><ul>\n<li><p>指定本地<code>dev</code>分支与远程<code>origin/dev</code>分支的链接(简化大量操作)</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> branch --set-upstream-to<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>origin/dev dev<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n<li><p>从本地推送分支，使用<code>git push origin name</code>，如果推送失败，先用git pull抓取远程的新提交(必需保证对应修改的是最新的)</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> push origin <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n<li><p>从远程抓取分支，使用<code>git pull</code>，如果有冲突，要先处理冲突</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> pull origin <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">因此，多人协作的工作模式通常是这样：\n\n1. 首先，可以试图用&#96;git push origin &#96;推送自己的修改；\n2. 如果推送失败，因为远程分支比本地更新，需要先用&#96;git pull&#96;试图合并；\n3. 如果合并有冲突，则解决冲突，并在本地提交；\n4. 没有冲突或者解决掉冲突后，再用&#96;git push origin &#96;推送就能成功！\n\n如果&#96;git pull&#96;提示&#96;no tracking information&#96;，则说明本地分支和远程分支的链接关系没有创建，用命令&#96;git branch --set-upstream-to  origin&#x2F;&#96;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<br/>\n\n<br/>\n\n<h2 id=\"冲突操作\"><a href=\"#冲突操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"冲突操作\"></a>冲突操作</h2><h3 id=\"分支合并冲突\"><a href=\"#分支合并冲突\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"分支合并冲突\"></a>分支合并冲突</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Yveltals/Picgo/git%E5%88%86%E6%94%AF.png\"></p>\n<p>两分支各自都分别有新的提交，Git无法执行“快速合并”，只能试图把各自的修改合并起来，但这种合并就可能会有冲突，如：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> merge feature1\nAuto-merging readme.txt\nCONFLICT <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>content<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>: Merge conflict <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> readme.txt\nAutomatic merge failed<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> fix conflicts and <span class=\"token keyword\">then</span> commit the result.<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>必须手动解决冲突后再提交(<code>git status</code>显示冲突文件)，可以直接查看<code>readme.txt</code>内容：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">Git is a distributed version control system.\nGit is free software distributed under the GPL.\nGit has a mutable index called stage.\nGit tracks changes of files.\n&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt; HEAD\nCreating a new branch is quick &amp; simple.\n&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;\nCreating a new branch is quick AND simple.\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; feature1<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>Git用<code>&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;</code>，<code>=======</code>，<code>&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;</code>标记不同分支的内容，我们修改如下后保存：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">Creating a new branch is quick and simple.<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>再提交：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> readme.txt \n$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> commit -m <span class=\"token string\">\"conflict fixed\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>main cf810e4<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> conflict fixed<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<br/>\n\n<br/>\n\n<h2 id=\"版本回退\"><a href=\"#版本回退\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"版本回退\"></a>版本回退</h2><p>在Git中，用<code>HEAD</code>表示当前版本，上个版本<code>HEAD^</code>，上上版本<code>HEAD^^</code>直到<code>HEAD~100</code>。</p>\n<p><code>git reset</code>把当前版本回退到上一个版本：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> reset --hard HEAD^\nHEAD is now at e475afc <span class=\"token function\">add</span> distributed<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>若想撤销回去，可以顺着往上找到对应的<code>commit id</code>如<code>1094adb...</code>：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> reset --hard 1094a\nHEAD is now at 83b0afe append GPL<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p><code>git reflog</code>查看命令历史，以便确定要回到未来的哪个版本：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> reflog\ne475afc HEAD@<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>: reset: moving to HEAD^\n1094adb <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>HEAD -<span class=\"token operator\">></span> main<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> HEAD@<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>: commit: append GPL\ne475afc HEAD@<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>: commit: <span class=\"token function\">add</span> distributed\neaadf4e HEAD@<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>: commit <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>initial<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>: wrote a readme <span class=\"token function\">file</span>\n从输出可知，<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">`</span>append GPL<span class=\"token variable\">`</span></span>的commit id是<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">`</span>1094adb<span class=\"token variable\">`</span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<br/>\n\n<br/>\n\n<h2 id=\"概念理解\"><a href=\"#概念理解\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"概念理解\"></a>概念理解</h2><h3 id=\"工作区和暂存区\"><a href=\"#工作区和暂存区\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"工作区和暂存区\"></a>工作区和暂存区</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Yveltals/Picgo/git%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%8C%BA.png\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"分支策略\"><a href=\"#分支策略\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"分支策略\"></a>分支策略</h3><p>在实际开发中，我们应该按照几个基本原则进行分支管理：</p>\n<p>首先，<code>main</code>分支应该是非常稳定的，也就是仅用来发布新版本，平时不能在上面干活；</p>\n<p>那在哪干活呢？干活都在<code>dev</code>分支上，也就是说，<code>dev</code>分支是不稳定的，到某个时候，比如1.0版本发布时，再把<code>dev</code>分支合并到<code>main</code>上，在<code>main</code>分支发布1.0版本；</p>\n<p>你和你的小伙伴们每个人都在<code>dev</code>分支上干活，每个人都有自己的分支，时不时地往<code>dev</code>分支上合并就可以了。</p>\n<p>所以，团队合作的分支看起来就像这样：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Yveltals/Picgo/git%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B.png\"></p>\n<p>Git核心概念<br><a href=\"https://lufficc.com/blog/the-core-conception-of-git#Git%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80\">https://lufficc.com/blog/the-core-conception-of-git#Git%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80</a></p>\n<p>Git廖雪峰<br><a href=\"https://www.liaoxuefeng.com/wiki/896043488029600/900003767775424\">https://www.liaoxuefeng.com/wiki/896043488029600/900003767775424</a></p>\n","text":"基本操作# 初始化 $ git init # 添加到暂存区 $ git add -A # 添加到分支 $ git commit -m \"deploy\" # 关联远程仓库，命名为origin # 1. ssh方式 $ git remote add origin git@github...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.1k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Software","slug":"Software","count":3,"path":"api/categories/Software.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Git","slug":"Git","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Git.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">基本操作</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%87%E6%8D%A2%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7\"><span class=\"toc-text\">切换本地用户</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%85%B3%E8%81%94%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93\"><span class=\"toc-text\">重新关联远程仓库</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDSubmodule\"><span class=\"toc-text\">下载Submodule</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#SSH%E5%AF%86%E9%92%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">SSH密钥</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">文件修改</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">查看文件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%92%A4%E9%94%80%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">撤销修改</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">文件删除</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%86%E6%94%AF%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">分支操作</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%86%E6%94%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">创建分支</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%90%88%E5%B9%B6%E5%88%86%E6%94%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">合并分支</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%86%E6%94%AF%E5%90%8C%E6%AD%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">分支同步</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%86%B2%E7%AA%81%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">冲突操作</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%86%E6%94%AF%E5%90%88%E5%B9%B6%E5%86%B2%E7%AA%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">分支合并冲突</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E5%9B%9E%E9%80%80\"><span class=\"toc-text\">版本回退</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%A6